Description: Free and open source FTP and FTPS Server.
 @PACKAGE@, starting from version 1.x, represents a complete rewrite
 of the historical FileZilla FTP server.
 .
 Key features include:
   - Support for FTP and secure FTPS protocols
   - Support for TLS 1.3 and enforcment of session resumption
   - Direct support for Let's Encrypt (TM) TLS certificates generation
   - Support for PKCS#11 secure tokens
   - Advanced user management to control access and permissions
   - Support for passive mode connections through NAT and firewall
   - Detailed logging for monitoring server activity and troubleshooting
   - Configurable transfer speed limits to balance server load
   - Remote administration capabilities for managing the server from anywhere
 .
 The server's architecture is built with security and portability in mind,
 catering to both novice and advanced users who need a dependable FTP/FTPS
 server solution. The project actively incorporates feedback and continues
 to evolve, ensuring compatibility with modern security standards and client
 requirements.
 .
 For more information, documentation, and support, visit the official FileZilla
 project website: https://filezilla-project.org/
